
### Publishing to GitHub

```bash
# On your local machine
mkdir citadel-pg-theme && cd citadel-pg-theme
git init

# Create the directory structure and add all files above
# Then:
git add .
git commit -m "Initial release of Citadel theme for Podcast Generator"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin git@github.com:VladdyC/citadel-pg-theme.git
git push -u origin main
